If you wanted a **"Gradient Background"** (very common in modern trading apps), you would change the `layout` to this:

```javascript
layout: {
    background: {
        type: ColorType.VerticalGradient,
        topColor: '#1e293b',
        bottomColor: '#0f172a',
    },
    textColor: '#ffffff',
}

```

